==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: focused
<hw>focused</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>focussed</asp>.]</altsp> <sn>1.</sn> <def>being in focus or brought
into focus; clearly delineated; -- of an image. Opposite of
<ant>unfocused</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>converging on a point; -- of light rays; <as>as,
<ex>focused</ex> light rays can set something afire</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>concentrated on or clustered around a central point
or purpose.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> centered, centred, centralized.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>focussed</ent>⟦br⟧
